You're bothering me and my friend.

29
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,480
Aside from my future wife,

30
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:38,280
I wouldn't touch any other woman.

31
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,920
You haven't been in a love?

32
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:01,160
Well,

33
