just now,

34
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:05,160
pretending to be a married couple

35
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:06,520
was purely

36
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,920
for getting Green Crystal.

37
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:09,520
Well,

38
00:02:09,920 --> 00:02:12,080
I couldn't possibly marry you.

39
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:16,320
