W-Who drank wine for you?

43
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:22,800
Narcissism.

44
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:24,840
Then give me your hand.

45
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:26,840
I'll try with my inner strength to see

46
