if I can force out the poisoned wine.

47
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:30,760
Although I'm not certain

48
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,360
whether that wine was poisoned,

49
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,480
or if it would only make one

50
