carbonated drink.

54
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:45,760
Carbonated drink?

55
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:50,400
(What am I saying?)

56
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:52,720
Give it a try.

57
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,320
Hedgehog.

58
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,880
What's wrong?

59
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,520
Do you smell that?

60
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:18,120
This was the smell that night

61
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,280
