67
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:39,000
We're taken in.

68
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:41,120
Leave now!

69
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,280
Hedgehog, are you fine?

70
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,440
Are you alright?

71
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,440
My strength

72
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,240
