73
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,720
Let's leave here now.

74
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:00,400
Let's go.

75
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:03,800
This isn't a place you can

76
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:06,160
