77
00:04:16,928 --> 00:04:19,440
(Tianshan Academy)
Who can understand profound chess?

78
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:22,080
After thousands of games,
one can understand the truth.

79
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:25,200
In Buddhism, there is endless fate.

80
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:28,280
But I just try to get ahead
in the next move.

81
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,000
Mr. Shi.

82
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:31,680
For this game of chess,

83
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,080
