84
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:40,880
Hedgehog, are you fine?

85
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,520
Zhao Wumian.

86
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:47,080
You can't escape today.

87
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:48,760
Yun Zhishui.

88
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:49,600
Help me!

89
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,040
Yun Zhishui.

90
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:52,400
You leave first.

91
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,560
I'll handle it.

92
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:56,880
No.

93
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:58,200
They are in danger now.

94
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:59,640
This is my territory.

95
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:01,400
Your junior Shi Tingyu

96
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:03,040
