99
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:09,200
Besides,

100
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,080
if you don't hurry back,

101
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:13,520
you may have
to collect your junior's corpse.

102
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:15,800
Yun Zhishui, help!

103
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:16,880
Yun Zhishui.

104
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:22,360
Don't touch that girl.

105
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:25,760
After so many years,

106
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:28,320
