you are anxious over a girl.

107
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:31,400
Then I really should

108
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:33,320
take good care of her.

109
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,600
This Beisu Qingfeng Powder is
so powerful

110
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:45,640
that even you, the top master...

111
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:50,080
It can't have such significant power

112
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:52,000
