113
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,080
It needs a conductor.

114
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:56,240
Conductor.

115
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:57,480
What's wrong?

116
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:58,960
Are you afraid it's poisoned?

117
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:09,320
So they had already
ingested the conductor.

118
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,760
They planned to lure us

119
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:14,240
into the Dark Capital.

120
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:17,520
What a good strategy!

121
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,440
Unexpectedly,

122
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:23,840
