123
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:27,480
It's truly an honor.

124
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:39,200
If I don't pretend to be poisoned,

125
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,200
how can I lure you to show up?

126
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:42,480
You six

127
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:45,360
