133
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:55,240
Except

134
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:56,920
you.

135
00:06:58,280 --> 00:06:59,840
You've messed with the wrong person,

136
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:02,240
