143
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,760
Attack him!

144
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:33,560
Leave one of your arms behind.

145
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:39,960
Right.

146
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:41,400
As long as you survive,

147
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,440
