148
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:44,040
Leave an arm behind,

149
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:45,080
then retreat.

150
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:46,120
This is not a loss.

151
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,400
Everyone.

152
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,960
Don't rush.

153
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,240
Rather than severing your arms,

154
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:56,320
