163
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:39,360
(Think about what to do next.)

164
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,320
(Say something.)

165
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,760
(Before,)

166
00:08:42,160 --> 00:08:43,520
(it seems I've told him)

167
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:44,840
(I am the eighth star.)

168
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:46,600
Leave.

169
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,160
I can last three more moves.

170
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:48,992
The code.

171
00:08:48,992 --> 00:08:49,520
Yes, the code.

172
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:50,240
Master Xu.

173
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:51,720
I am

174
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:54,400
