177
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:00,840
Wait, wait, Master Xu.

178
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:01,720
I...

179
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:03,960
I am the eighth star

180
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,400
of the Big Dipper Sect.

181
