199
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:48,160
Whether it's true

200
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,360
or false,

201
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:50,760
anyway,

202
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:53,120
